attr.title: PokeMMO
attr.desc: Unofficial port of PokeMMO for PortMaster-compatible devices. PokeMMO is a fan-made multiplayer online game that brings together various Pok√©mon generations in a single MMO experience.
attr.inst: Download the portable version of the PokeMMO client from https://pokemmo.com/en/downloads/portable. Extract the ZIP and copy both the PokeMMO.exe file and the data folder into /roms/ports/pokemmo.
